    h3 What is Ogre?
    p Ogre is a web client (service) that translates spatial files into <a href="http://geojson.org">GeoJSON</a> using the <a href="http://www.gdal.org/ogr2ogr.html">ogr2ogr</a> command line tool for use in JavaScript web applications and frameworks.

